reviews.text: The staff was professional, knowledgeable, and attentive to my needs. The clinic has a calming atmosphere, and the practitioners take the time to explain each step of the process. Overall, I had a great experience!

Amazing experience with Aimin TCM slimming service! The acupuncture treatments are highly effective, and the staff are incredibly friendly and professional. They always make me feel comfortable and well taken care of. I've seen great progress and highly recommend their services to anyone looking for a holistic and natural way to slim down. Thank you, Aimin :)

The service provided is professional and holistic in improving my overall well-being. The staff are friendly, knowledgeable and attentive, making the entire experience relaxing and rejuvenating for me.

The treatments at Aimin are quite good, and the staff are quite professional. However, booking sessions after signing a package can be challenging (even booking 1 to 2 months ahead). Weekend morning slots are often reserved for regulars, making it difficult for others to get appointments at preferred times. If you have a fixed schedule, this could be frustrating. While the quality of service is decent, I hope they can improve their booking system to be more inclusive and fair for all package holders.
Tried the slimming massage at Kensington. Staff are friendly. Explained all available treatments patiently. Will be taking the package as it seemed effective during trial.
